      "references": "[Su11] Sudakov, Benny, A conjecture of Erd\\H{o}s on graph Ramsey numbers. Adv. Math. (2011), 601-609.",
      "remarks": "A question of Erd\\H{o}s and Graham. The weaker question of whether\\[R(G) \\leq 2^{O(m^{1/2})}\\]is the subject of [546]. (This is true, and was proved by Sudakov \\cite{Su11}.)\n\nLouisD in the comments has noted this fails for small $m$ (in particular for $2\\leq m\\leq 5$ and $7\\leq m\\leq 9$).\n\nThis problem is #10 in Ramsey Theory in the graphs problem collection."
    },
